<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About Us – Avanza</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { session: session, page: 'about' }) %>
    <main class="flex-fill">

      <section class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="mb-4">About Us</h1>

        <p class="lead">
          Avanza is dedicated to helping students thrive academically through personalized
          coaching, executive function skill-building, and compassionate support.
        </p>

        <p>
          We believe every student has the ability to succeed with the right guidance.
          Our coaches work
          1-on-1 with students to improve organization, strengthen study habits, and build confidence.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-primary text-white py-5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
              <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Roberto Hasbun" class="rounded-circle border border-5 border-white shadow-lg mb-3 mb-md-0" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-9">
              <h2 class="fw-bold">A Note from Roberto Hasbun, Founder</h2>
              <p class="lead">"I started Avanza with a single vision: to bridge the gap between a student's potential and their academic achievement. Our journey is built on personal experience and a commitment to genuine, transformative mentorship."</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="container py-5">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold text-success">Our Mission</h3>
            <p>To empower every student with the essential executive function and academic skills needed to navigate their education and achieve their college and career goals independently.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold text-primary">Our Vision</h3>
            <p>To be the leading platform for personalized academic coaching, creating a global community of self-directed, resilient, and successful students who advance their own futures.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold" style="color: #FF8C00;">Our Values</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i> **Empathy**: Understanding the student's unique challenges.</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i> **Excellence**: Delivering the highest quality coaching.</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i> **Empowerment**: Cultivating self-advocacy and independence.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="container py-5 bg-light">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">What Makes EduEmpowered Different?</h2>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h4 class="fw-bold">The Empowered Foundation</h4>
            <p>Our methodology focuses heavily on the "how," not just the "what." We build a strong foundation of **Executive Function Skills**—planning, prioritization, and sustained attention—that serves students long after their high school years, making them truly college and career ready.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h4 class="fw-bold">Holistic, Mentorship-Driven Approach</h4>
            <p>We combine personalized coaching with a mentorship philosophy. Our coaches are not just tutors; they are guides dedicated to developing the student's full potential, ensuring emotional and mental well-being alongside academic rigor.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="container py-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Meet Our Team</h2>
        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center" id="roberto">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Roberto Hasbun" class="rounded-circle mb-3 shadow-sm">
                <h5 class="fw-bold">Roberto Hasbun</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Founder & Lead Coach</p>
                <p>Specializes in holistic college admissions consulting and executive function remediation.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">View Full CV & Reviews</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center" id="jane">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Jane Doe" class="rounded-circle mb-3 shadow-sm">
                <h5 class="fw-bold">Jane Doe</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Executive Function Coach</p>
                <p>Expert in developing time management, organizational, and study strategies for high-achievers.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">View Full CV & Reviews</a>
            </div>
            </div>
      </section>

    </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>